snippet.title: Yume Nikki Fangame playthrough - Oneiro
snippet.description:
Apparently people keep asking me if I have this game. Yes, I do. I don't feel comfortable sharing a reupload (at least in a widespread fashion), so I'll just make a walkthrough video.
Content warning:
- Blood

Read more about this fangame: https://ynfg.yume.wiki/Oneiro
[Download unavailable]
Check out the Dream Diary Jam 2 page!: https://itch.io/jam/dream-diary-jam-2-yume-nikki-jam-
